steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"bn1b","text":"hPSCs are cultured on MEFs as described in the collection \"Thawing, Passaging, and Freezing of hPSCs on MEFS\" dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.b4msqu6e","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"UNDERLINE","offset":110,"length":41}],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":110,"length":41}],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"link","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"guid":"B24371750A4A11ED9C510A58A9FEAC02","url":"https://dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.b4msqu6e"}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"2nqcc","text":"0.5 million hPSCs are nucleofected as described in “Nucleofection of hPSCs\" dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.b4pcqviw","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"UNDERLINE","offset":76,"length":41}],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":76,"length":41}],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"link","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"guid":"552572900A4A11ED9C510A58A9FEAC02","url":"https://dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.b4pcqviw"}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"oksn","text":"Seed 1/100, 1/500 of cells post-nucleofection into one well of a 6-well plate containing hPSCs medium with Rock inhibitor. Prepare at least 2 wells for each seeding density as replicates. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"aumdl","text":"Change medium at day 3, 6, 8, 10, and then daily until colonies grow to medium size.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4dfb3","text":"Perform Alkaline phosphatase (AP) staining as described in “Pluripotency markers staining” dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.b4yyqxxw","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"UNDERLINE","offset":91,"length":41}],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":91,"length":41}],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"link","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"guid":"3DB89C2C0A4E11ED9C510A58A9FEAC02","url":"https://dx.doi.org/10.17504/protocols.io.b4yyqxxw"}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"c7i3d","text":"Image the entire stained well with ChemiDoc (Bio-Rad). Use a white cardboard as background. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
